text: Brienz/Brinzauls () was a municipality in the district of Albula in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2015 the former municipalities of Brienz/Brinzauls, Alvaneu, Alvaschein, Mon, Stierva, Surava and Tiefencastel merged into the new municipality of Albula/Alvra. ==Other websites== * Official Website Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
